1.0.name: wordpress/oneid-login
1.0.description:
OneID Sign In is an easy-to-integrate digital identity service that makes it one-click easy for users to sign into your site.

Benefits for you

  • Reduced costs: No more lost password support is needed, saving you time and money.
  • Secured accounts: Layered security protects customers (and you) against breaches and attacks, like phishing and malware.
  • Mobile acceleration: One-click sign in makes it easy for users to log in while on their mobile devices.

For your users, OneID offers

  • Privacy: OneID does not track any individual user behavior – and certainly won’t share it.
  • Security: OneID secures user information using three separate cryptographic combinations across multiple devices.
  • Convenience: OneID removes the hassle of having to remember user names and passwords.

And along with all those great benefits to you and your users, with this pl
